  {
    "startTime": 424.0,
    "endTime": 425.0,
    "text": "We'll get a bit closer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.0,
    "endTime": 430.0,
    "text": "And then up there, there's a little food truck or a little food place where we're gonna get a lobster roll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.0,
    "endTime": 431.0,
    "text": "Should be yummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.0,
    "endTime": 440.0,
    "text": "So I know this is a food video, but this is a pretty cool shot of this lighthouse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.0,
    "endTime": 443.0,
    "text": "I'll have to do a little bit of research about it later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.0,
    "endTime": 445.0,
    "text": "But here we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.0,
    "endTime": 449.0,
    "text": "You can see what I think is the Atlantic Ocean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.0,
    "endTime": 450.0,
    "text": "It could just be a large bay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.0,
    "endTime": 451.0,
    "text": "I'll have to check a map."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.0,
    "endTime": 455.0,
    "text": "But we're here on the Eastern seaboard, we would call it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.0,
    "endTime": 458.0,
    "text": "Making a food video where I'm not actually eating anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.0,
    "endTime": 460.0,
    "text": "We'll get back to that in just a sec."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.0,
    "endTime": 462.0,
    "text": "Okay, I'm just taking a selfie for Jen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.0,
    "endTime": 466.0,
    "text": "I decided if I was on a trip without her, I should at least send her some pictures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.0,
    "endTime": 467.0,
    "text": "So here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.0,
    "endTime": 468.0,
    "text": "Oop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.0,
    "endTime": 471.0,
    "text": "Almost dropped my phone because of the suntan lotion on my hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.0,
    "endTime": 474.0,
    "text": "There we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.0,
    "endTime": 477.0,
    "text": "Okay, so we're here at this little trailer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.0,
    "endTime": 480.0,
    "text": "I called it a food truck, but it's a trailer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.0,
    "endTime": 485.0,
    "text": "And we're gonna get a lobster roll, which is apparently a pretty common thing to get when you're in Maine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.0,
    "endTime": 488.0,
    "text": "I think Brent's gonna pay for them again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.0,
    "endTime": 489.0,
    "text": "We'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.0,
    "endTime": 490.0,
    "text": "What can I get for ya?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.0,
    "endTime": 494.0,
    "text": "I say we go with a couple lobster rolls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.0,
    "endTime": 495.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.0,
    "endTime": 497.0,
    "text": "And since we're in Maine, we gotta do the Maine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.0,
    "endTime": 499.0,
    "text": "Yeah, two Maine lobster rolls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.0,
    "endTime": 500.0,
    "text": "Yeah, we got two sizes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.0,
    "endTime": 501.0,
    "text": "We have a four and a half ounce and a six."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.0,
    "endTime": 502.0,
    "text": "How hungry are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.0,
    "endTime": 503.0,
    "text": "The smaller one for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.0,
    "endTime": 503.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.0,
    "endTime": 505.0,
    "text": "Smaller one for me as well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.0,
    "endTime": 507.0,
    "text": "We're kind of on a tour of food, so we don't want to eat too much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.0,
    "endTime": 510.0,
    "text": "So it says for the Maine one, just mayo and chives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.0,
    "endTime": 510.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.0,
    "endTime": 511.0,
    "text": "Does it come with any butter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.0,
    "endTime": 513.0,
    "text": "We can put butter on anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.0,
    "endTime": 514.0,
    "text": "Please do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.0,
    "endTime": 516.0,
    "text": "All right, I'll get that receipt printed for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.0,
    "endTime": 516.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.0,
    "endTime": 517.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.0,
    "endTime": 518.0,
    "text": "And I'll get you those drinks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.0,
    "endTime": 518.0,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.0,
    "endTime": 521.0,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 521.0,
    "endTime": 522.0,
    "text": "Here's the waters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.0,
    "endTime": 525.0,
    "text": "Let's get our moxies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 525.0,
    "endTime": 527.0,
    "text": "You guys had moxie before?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.0,
    "endTime": 528.0,
    "text": "I've had it before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.0,
    "endTime": 528.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.0,
    "endTime": 532.0,
    "text": "So we're gonna- We're gonna see if I like it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.0,
    "endTime": 535.0,
    "text": "Let us know where you fall on the great debate here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.0,
    "endTime": 536.0,
    "text": "Do you like it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.0,
    "endTime": 537.0,
    "text": "I love it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.0,
    "endTime": 538.0,
    "text": "You do, really?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.0,
    "endTime": 539.0,
    "text": "You'll be number 49."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.0,
    "endTime": 539.0,
    "text": "We'll just call it a morning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.0,
    "endTime": 540.0,
    "text": "Okay, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.0,
    "endTime": 541.0,
    "text": "Enjoy guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.0,
    "endTime": 545.0,
    "text": "I've had this for about 20 years and it's not as bad as I thought."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.0,
    "endTime": 546.0,
    "text": "No, this is really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 546.0,
    "endTime": 548.0,
    "text": "So I'm trying moxie by the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.0,
    "endTime": 551.0,
    "text": "So I, sorry, I stopped recording."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.0,
    "endTime": 554.0,
    "text": "So you didn't see me open the can and hear the nice sound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.0,
    "endTime": 555.0,
    "text": "I'll make the sound for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.0,
    "endTime": 557.0,
    "text": "It's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.0,
    "endTime": 561.0,
    "text": "It's very sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.0,
    "endTime": 564.0,
    "text": "It's like a traditional soda."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.0,
    "endTime": 576.0,
    "text": "I was expecting something that was a little different, but it says on here distinctively different, but it really tastes like just a regular sweet, almost like a root beer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.0,
    "endTime": 578.0,
    "text": "I was gonna say, it has a hint of like root beer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.0,
    "endTime": 582.0,
    "text": "So I don't know, is that sassafras or something like that, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.0,
    "endTime": 582.0,
    "text": "It's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.0,
    "endTime": 584.0,
    "text": "I would drink it again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.0,
    "endTime": 587.0,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.0,
    "endTime": 589.0,
    "text": "Enjoy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.0,
    "endTime": 589.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.0,
    "endTime": 594.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 595.0,
    "endTime": 599.0,
    "text": "Okay, so this is a lobster roll."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.0,
    "endTime": 606.0,
    "text": "It looks kind of like a fancy, fancy bun with lots of lobster in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.0,
    "endTime": 608.0,
    "text": "And then some potato chips."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.0,
    "endTime": 611.0,
    "text": "Potato chips are good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 611.0,
    "endTime": 612.0,
    "text": "They're a bit salty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.0,
    "endTime": 614.0,
    "text": "I noticed there's a fork."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.0,
    "endTime": 615.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.0,
    "endTime": 617.0,
    "text": "There's also lemon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.0,
    "endTime": 623.0,
    "text": "I'm gonna assume like traditional seafood, I should put some lemon on this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.0,
    "endTime": 629.0,
    "text": "And then is the fork for like newbies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.0,
    "endTime": 633.0,
    "text": "I think it can get pretty messy, so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.0,
    "endTime": 635.0,
    "text": "I think I just, I gotta just take a bite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.0,
    "endTime": 636.0,
    "text": "So here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.0,
    "endTime": 639.0,
    "text": "My first bite."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.0,
    "endTime": 646.0,
    "text": "Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.0,
    "endTime": 651.0,
    "text": "Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.0,
    "endTime": 652.0,
    "text": "That is very fresh seafood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 653.0,
    "endTime": 658.0,
    "text": "Like where I live, far from the ocean, we don't get fresh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.0,
    "endTime": 660.0,
    "text": "This is, this is very good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.0,
    "endTime": 661.0,
    "text": "You can tell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.0,
    "endTime": 663.0,
    "text": "I didn't know you could tell that easily."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.0,
    "endTime": 669.0,
    "text": "And I'm not the biggest lobster fan, but I mean, they didn't skimp on the lobster meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670.0,
    "endTime": 671.0,
    "text": "That means they didn't hold back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 672.0,
    "endTime": 675.0,
    "text": "They didn't, they gave us a lot of lobster in this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 676.0,
    "endTime": 678.0,
    "text": "So I'm gonna try it just with a fork here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.0,
    "endTime": 680.0,
    "text": "It's also very buttery."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.0,
    "endTime": 684.0,
    "text": "There's like butter on my hands from eating it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 684.0,
    "endTime": 687.0,
    "text": "And it's very messy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 689.0,
    "endTime": 694.0,
    "text": "Sorry for talking with my mouth full, but it's very hard to eat without it falling apart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.0,
    "endTime": 697.0,
    "text": "Mm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 699.0,
    "endTime": 700.0,
    "text": "Good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 702.0,
    "endTime": 702.0,
    "text": "Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.0,
    "endTime": 704.0,
    "text": "It's the best thing I've eaten today so far."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705.0,
    "endTime": 706.0,
    "text": "Better than the donuts?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 706.0,
    "endTime": 708.0,
    "text": "Better than the chocolate sea salt donut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.0,
    "endTime": 712.0,
    "text": "So there's a couple of words I would use to describe this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.0,
    "endTime": 714.0,
    "text": "I, I demolished it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 714.0,
    "endTime": 717.0,
    "text": "That means like this is Brent's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.0,
    "endTime": 720.0,
    "text": "This is mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 720.0,
    "endTime": 721.0,
    "text": "It's gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.0,
    "endTime": 722.0,
    "text": "Or I destroyed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 722.0,
    "endTime": 724.0,
    "text": "That's kind of a newer word we use sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.0,
    "endTime": 725.0,
    "text": "Like I just destroyed it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.0,
    "endTime": 728.0,
    "text": "But that was yummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.0,
    "endTime": 729.0,
    "text": "I don't think I'm gonna eat the chips."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729.0,
    "endTime": 735.0,
    "text": "I'm not a big fan of chips, but that was really, really good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 736.0,
    "endTime": 737.0,
    "text": "Delicious, scrumptious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.0,
    "endTime": 738.0,
    "text": "I can't think of any other words."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 740.0,
    "endTime": 744.0,
    "text": "So I said I wasn't gonna eat my potato chips, but I didn't wanna let them go to waste."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 745.0,
    "endTime": 748.0,
    "text": "When you let something go to waste, it means you don't eat it and you throw it away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.0,
    "endTime": 750.0,
    "text": "And I just couldn't let them go to waste."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 750.0,
    "endTime": 751.0,
    "text": "They are yummy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 751.0,
    "endTime": 753.0,
    "text": "I was just feeling kind of full."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 753.0,
    "endTime": 757.0,
    "text": "When you eat a lot of food, especially the lobster roll, you can feel full."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757.0,
    "endTime": 760.0,
    "text": "But yeah, I can't let these go to waste, so I'm gonna eat them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 760.0,
    "endTime": 763.0,
    "text": "Okay, so we're on our way to get a whoopie pie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 764.0,
    "endTime": 764.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.0,
    "endTime": 765.0,
    "text": "Whoopie pie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.0,
    "endTime": 766.0,
    "text": "Place called Wicked Whoopie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 767.0,
    "endTime": 770.0,
    "text": "And I think whoopie pies are very famous in Maine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 770.0,
    "endTime": 772.0,
    "text": "Have you ever had a whoopie pie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 772.0,
    "endTime": 773.0,
    "text": "I think you brought me one last year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 773.0,
    "endTime": 774.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 774.0,
    "endTime": 780.0,
    "text": "It was really good, but I'm looking forward to, is this gonna be fresh made, or it's gonna be similar to what I had last year?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 780.0,
    "endTime": 782.0,
    "text": "No, it'll be a lot fresher than last year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 782.0,
    "endTime": 783.0,
    "text": "Okay, well, hopefully it's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785.0,
    "endTime": 786.0,
    "text": "Is that it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 786.0,
    "endTime": 788.0,
    "text": "That's it, Wicked Whoopie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 788.0,
    "endTime": 790.0,
    "text": "Okay, here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 790.0,
    "endTime": 795.0,
    "text": "In Maine, when we say something is really good, we might say it's wicked good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.0,
    "endTime": 797.0,
    "text": "Oh, so that's why it says Wicked Whoopies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 797.0,
    "endTime": 798.0,
    "text": "Wicked good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.0,
    "endTime": 799.0,
    "text": "Ah, I see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 799.0,
    "endTime": 799.0,
    "text": "Very cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 801.0,
    "endTime": 806.0,
    "text": "Okay, so there's a lot of flavors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 807.0,
    "endTime": 809.0,
    "text": "I see a lot of chocolate flavors over there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 809.0,
    "endTime": 810.0,
    "text": "That's probably where I'm gonna go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811.0,
    "endTime": 814.0,
    "text": "Okay, so I just noticed they have mint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 814.0,
    "endTime": 816.0,
    "text": "So it looks like chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 817.0,
    "endTime": 819.0,
    "text": "And then the inside probably has like a mint flavor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 819.0,
    "endTime": 822.0,
    "text": "I might go for that, because I do like mint chocolate chip ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 822.0,
    "endTime": 823.0,
    "text": "So we'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 823.0,
    "endTime": 825.0,
    "text": "And then when I saw this, I said, hold the phone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 826.0,
    "endTime": 832.0,
    "text": "In English, when you say hold the phone, it means stop whatever you're thinking about, because I might be changing my mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.0,
    "endTime": 833.0,
    "text": "So, hmm, mint?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 834.0,
    "endTime": 836.0,
    "text": "And Brent, these are on me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 836.0,
    "endTime": 840.0,
    "text": "In English, when you say something's on you, it means you're paying for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.0,
    "endTime": 843.0,
    "text": "So Brent bought other stuff today, so this one's on me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.0,
    "endTime": 846.0,
    "text": "Would you like a bag for these?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 846.0,
    "endTime": 847.0,
    "text": "No, we're gonna eat them right away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 848.0,
    "endTime": 848.0,
    "text": "All righty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.0,
    "endTime": 850.0,
    "text": "Can we eat them at one of those tables over there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 850.0,
    "endTime": 851.0,
    "text": "Of course you can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.0,
    "endTime": 852.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.0,
    "endTime": 852.0,
    "text": "Meat 23."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 853.0,
    "endTime": 853.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 853.0,
    "endTime": 855.0,
    "text": "I might need to punch my code in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 855.0,
    "endTime": 857.0,
    "text": "Nope, you are all set."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 857.0,
    "endTime": 857.0,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 857.0,
    "endTime": 858.0,
    "text": "Awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 859.0,
    "endTime": 860.0,
    "text": "Do you sell much of that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 860.0,
    "endTime": 860.0,
    "text": "Yeah, we do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 861.0,
    "endTime": 861.0,
    "text": "In the summer?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 861.0,
    "endTime": 868.0,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm not a gingerbread fan, but you would be surprised at people that come in specifically for the fall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.0,
    "endTime": 868.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.0,
    "endTime": 869.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 869.0,
    "endTime": 870.0,
    "text": "Can I get a receipt?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.0,
    "endTime": 870.0,
    "text": "You bet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 870.0,
    "endTime": 872.0,
    "text": "Do you have a lot of Canadians that come in here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 872.0,
    "endTime": 873.0,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 873.0,
    "endTime": 873.0,
    "text": "Okay, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 873.0,
    "endTime": 875.0,
    "text": "I'm not the only one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.0,
    "endTime": 877.0,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 877.0,
    "endTime": 877.0,
    "text": "Enjoy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 878.0,
    "endTime": 879.0,
    "text": "Okay, let's find a table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.0,
    "endTime": 880.0,
    "text": "Right in the corner here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.0,
    "endTime": 883.0,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 883.0,
    "endTime": 886.0,
    "text": "It's time for the grand opening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 887.0,
    "endTime": 890.0,
    "text": "Sorry, grand opening's usually when a store opens, not when you open stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 891.0,
    "endTime": 892.0,
    "text": "Here's the opening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 892.0,
    "endTime": 894.0,
    "text": "So you definitely went with the classic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 894.0,
    "endTime": 895.0,
    "text": "Oh, it's very minty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 896.0,
    "endTime": 899.0,
    "text": "Yeah, it's like, I did go mint, but it's the classic look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.0,
    "endTime": 900.0,
    "text": "Yes, it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 900.0,
    "endTime": 901.0,
    "text": "You could be mistaken."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 901.0,
    "endTime": 903.0,
    "text": "I thought it was vanilla in the middle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 904.0,
    "endTime": 906.0,
    "text": "So you might not have to brush your teeth tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 906.0,
    "endTime": 907.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 907.0,
    "endTime": 908.0,
    "text": "Because of the mint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 908.0,
    "endTime": 909.0,
    "text": "Because you think it's kind of like toothpaste?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 911.0,
    "endTime": 911.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 912.0,
    "endTime": 918.0,
    "text": "Oh, it's minty, definitely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 918.0,
    "endTime": 924.0,
    "text": "It's cakier, so I thought the outside would be a little bit more like a brownie, like a little more dense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 924.0,
    "endTime": 928.0,
    "text": "It's actually a lot cakier, light and fluffy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 929.0,
    "endTime": 933.0,
    "text": "The center is, there's a lot of icing sugar in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 933.0,
    "endTime": 934.0,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 934.0,
    "endTime": 939.0,
    "text": "It tastes a little bit like the icing on a cake, like a cake that you would eat for your birthday, so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 940.0,
    "endTime": 942.0,
    "text": "So how many of these do you think you could eat in a sitting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 944.0,
    "endTime": 945.0,
    "text": "Three, four?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 945.0,
    "endTime": 945.0,
    "text": "Half."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 945.0,
    "endTime": 948.0,
    "text": "Yeah, once we stop the camera."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 948.0,
    "endTime": 950.0,
    "text": "I don't think I can eat more than half, and I will eat the rest tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 950.0,
    "endTime": 952.0,
    "text": "It is yummy, very, very good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 953.0,
    "endTime": 954.0,
    "text": "How's yours?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 954.0,
    "endTime": 955.0,
    "text": "It's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 955.0,
    "endTime": 957.0,
    "text": "I love chocolate, so the more chocolate, the better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 957.0,
    "endTime": 958.0,
    "text": "Chocolate's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 958.0,
    "endTime": 961.0,
    "text": "Chocolate cake, chocolate filling, my stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 961.0,
    "endTime": 963.0,
    "text": "You can't go wrong, that's a good phrase for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 963.0,
    "endTime": 967.0,
    "text": "You can't go wrong means you made a good decision, or that's a good decision to make."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 967.0,
    "endTime": 968.0,
    "text": "So, I would get it again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 969.0,
    "endTime": 972.0,
    "text": "And we should ask, like, what would you get?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 972.0,
    "endTime": 973.0,
    "text": "Yeah, what would you get?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 973.0,
    "endTime": 974.0,
    "text": "Go with the mint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 974.0,
    "endTime": 975.0,
    "text": "Peanut butter?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 975.0,
    "endTime": 975.0,
    "text": "Double chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 976.0,
    "endTime": 976.0,
    "text": "Peanut butter's a good one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 976.0,
    "endTime": 982.0,
    "text": "I know, I'll have to try that next time, in two years when I'm back, because next year hopefully Brent's in Canada, we'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 983.0,
    "endTime": 984.0,
    "text": "Anyways, good choice, thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 985.0,
    "endTime": 987.0,
    "text": "I said thanks, but I paid for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 988.0,
    "endTime": 989.0,
    "text": "Where'd it go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 990.0,
    "endTime": 991.0,
    "text": "So, I ate the whole thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 991.0,
    "endTime": 996.0,
    "text": "I wasn't planning to eat the whole thing, but it really hit the spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 996.0,
    "endTime": 1005.0,
    "text": "In English, when you say something hits the spot, it means you ate something or drank something that was, like, exactly what you needed in that moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1005.0,
    "endTime": 1007.0,
    "text": "So, this hit the spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1007.0,
    "endTime": 1009.0,
    "text": "It was the mint, I really like the mint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1009.0,
    "endTime": 1013.0,
    "text": "So, we should check back in in 20 minutes and see how you're feeling, because..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1013.0,
    "endTime": 1019.0,
    "text": "I'll probably be sleeping on the couch at Brent's house, because I think I'm gonna have a bit of a sugar overload, but yeah, that definitely hit the spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1020.0,
    "endTime": 1028.0,
    "text": "Well, hey, thanks for watching this little English lesson where I ate some food and hopefully I described it in enough ways that you were able to learn some English words and phrases."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1028.0,
    "endTime": 1038.0,
    "text": "I know it wasn't a traditional English lesson, but it certainly was fun to have you along as Brent and I toured a little bit of Maine and tried some of the food and one drink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1038.0,
    "endTime": 1039.0,
    "text": "So, anyways, thanks for watching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1039.0,
    "endTime": 1048.0,
    "text": " Remember, if this is your first time here, don't forget to click that subscribe button, give me a thumbs up, and if you have some more time, why don't you stick around and watch another English lesson?"
  }
]